API Key: Replace "YOUR_FINNHUB_API_KEY" with your actual Finnhub API key.

Authentication: Create a config.yaml file with user credentials (example provided below).

Dependencies: Install required libraries with:

pip install streamlit streamlit-authenticator finnhub-python ccxt pmdarima plotly pandas numpy sqlite3

Run the App: Use streamlit run financial_analyzer.py to start the tool locally.

Sample config.yaml
Save this as config.yaml in the same directory as the script (update with secure credentials):

